item.confluence.treasure_magnet.info: The Treasure Magnet is a post-Skeletron accessory which increases the pickup range of items from 2.625 tiles to 12 tiles while equipped.
item.confluence.treasure_magnet.info2: When an item is within its range, before directly flying to the player, it will hover a few blocks off the ground.
item.confluence.treasure_magnet.info3: The Treasure Magnet has a 1/5 (20%) chance of being found in Shadow Chests in the Underworld, as well as a 1/5 (20%) chance of being found in Obsidian Lock Boxes obtained from Obsidian Crates and Hellstone Crates.
item.confluence.trifold_map.info: The Trifold Map is a Hardmode immunity accessory that grants the player immunity to the Confused debuff.
item.confluence.trifold_map.info2: It has a 1/100 (1%) / 1/50 (2%) chance to drop from Clowns, Giant Bats, Light Mummies.
item.confluence.trifold_map.info3: It is one of the ingredients required to craft The Plan, which is a crafting material required to make the Ankh Charm, an accessory further required to make the Ankh Shield.
item.confluence.tsunami_in_a_bottle.info: The Tsunami in a Bottle is an accessory which can be found in Wooden, Iron, Pearlwood, and Mythril Crates.

Similar to the Cloud in a Bottle, it allows the player to double-jump. Instead of a cloud beneath the player's feet, it creates burst of water when jumping. The Tsunami jump goes 7 tiles into the air, totalling 13 tiles when put together with the first jump.
item.confluence.tungsten_watch.info: The Tungsten Watch is a mid-tier watch.
item.confluence.tungsten_watch.info2: The Silver Watch is the alternative to it. When equipped in an accessory slot or held in the inventory, a clock icon will appear in the upper-right corner of the playing screen, revealing the in-game time accurate to the last half-hour.
item.confluence.tungsten_watch.info3: Half an hour of Terraria game time is equivalent to a minute of real-world time.
item.confluence.tungsten_watch.info4: The Tungsten Watch can be used to craft the 3 Second Timer.
item.confluence.vitamins.info: Vitamins are a Hardmode immunity accessory that grants the player immunity to the Weak debuff.
item.confluence.vitamins.info2: It has a 1/100 (1%) / 1/50 (2%) chance to drop from Corruptors and Floaty Grosses.
item.confluence.vitamins.info3: Vitamins are one of the ingredients required to make the Armor Bracing, which is a crafting material required to make the Ankh Charm, an accessory further required to make the Ankh Shield.
item.confluence.warrior_emblem.info: The Warrior Emblem is a Hardmode accessory that increases melee damage by 15%. It has a 1/4 (25%) chance to drop from the Wall of Flesh.
item.confluence.water_walking_boots.info: Water Walking Boots are an accessory that allows a player to walk on water, honey, and shimmer.
The player moves across these liquids at normal speed without sinking.
They do not allow walking on lava.
When the player is on a liquid, they may press Down Key to fall through the liquid, similar to a platform.
Water Walking Boots have a 1/10 (10%) chance of being obtained from Water Chests, Ocean Crates, and Seaside Crates.
item.confluence.water_walking_boots.tool: Provides the ability to walk on water & honey
item.confluence.weather_radio.info: The Weather Radio is an informational accessory that displays the current weather and wind speed on the Surface, even if the player is in the Underground, Cavern, or Underworld layers.
item.confluence.weather_radio.info2: The Weather Radio is one of the three parts necessary to make the Fish Finder, with the others being the Sextant and the Fisherman's Pocket Guide, and as such is a required ingredient in crafting the Shellphone.

Jump height is oddly reduced when underwater, reducing total underwater jump height from 19 blocks (8 + 11 from Blizzard jump) to 16 blocks (7 + 9 from Blizzard jump).
item.confluence.worm_scarf.info: The Worm Scarf is a pre-Hardmode accessory that reduces incoming damage by 17%.
item.confluence.worm_scarf.info2: This damage reduction from this item is calculated after defense is applied.
item.confluence.worm_scarf.info3: The Worm Scarf is always dropped from the Eater of Worlds' Treasure Bag in Expert Mode.
item.confluence.xenon_moss_fishing_bobbe: Increases fishing power,Your bobber now glows
item.confluence.yellow_horseshoe_balloon: The Yellow Horseshoe Balloon is an accessory that grants immunity to fall damage, increases jump height by 75%, grants a double-jump, and grants +0.05 luck.
The height of the first jump is increased from 6 blocks to 10.5 blocks, while the double-jump's height is increased from 15 blocks to 26.5 blocks, reaching a total of 37 blocks with both jumps.
